@yangjunpro I recently implemented the distributed DL training method based on the paper you mentioned. Here is the details: #11071 .
But there are some problems with my implementation: the training loss decreases at the begining but will increases dramatically suddenly after the ps params do several updates.
Could you share some ideas of your implementation? Thanks.

